<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="basic_iosbad" id="basic_iosbad">basic_ios::bad</a></h2>
<div class="level2">
<pre class="cpp code cpp"><span class="kw4">bool</span> bad<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
Returns <code>true</code> if a non-recoverable error has occurred on the associated stream. Specifically, returns <code>true</code> if <code>badbit</code> is set in <code>rdstate()</code>.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "basic_ios::bad" [1-214] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2"><a name="parameters" id="parameters">Parameters</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

(none)
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "Parameters" [215-242] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="return_value" id="return_value">Return value</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

<code>true</code> if the stream has a non-recoverable error occurred.
</p>

</div>
